# How to Go Viral

Nikita Bier - Youtube Talk
## Users use apps to
  - coz its cheaper
  - for distraction
  - to connect with people

1. teens are viral early adopters - you want viral growth
1. should push product up to a point - aka tipping point in 90 days
1. low costs for production eg grants or free cloud resources
1. get good at quickly validating your ideas - product market fit
1. business of apps - getting customers is hard for consumer apps
1. show value quickly: can a 5th grader use it...

